gurmukhi: ਅਗੰਜ ਅਾਦਿ ਦੇਵ ਹੈਂ ਅਭੰਜ ਭੰਜ ਜਾਨੀਅੈਂ ॥
transliteration: Agadj Aadh Dev Hain Abhanj Bhanj Jaanooain||
translation: The Primal Lord is Eternal, He may be comprehended as the breaker of the Unbreakable.

gurmukhi: ਅਭੂਤ ਭੂਤ ਹੈਂ ਸਦਾ ਅਗੰਜ ਗੰਜ ਮਾਨੀਅੈਂ ॥
transliteration: Abhoot Bhoot Hain Sadaa Agadj Gadj Maanooain||
translation: He is ever both Gross and Subtle, He assails the Unassailable.

gurmukhi: ਅਦੇਵ ਦੇਵ ਹੈਂ ਸਦਾ ਅਭੇਬ ਭੇਵ ਨਾਥ ਹੈਂ ॥
transliteration: Adev Dev Hain Sadaa Abhev Bhev Naath Hain||
translation: He is both god and demon, He is the Lord of both covert and overt.

gurmukhi: ਸਮਸਤ ਸਿੱਧ ਬ੍ਰਿਧਿ ਦਾ ਸਦੀਵ ਸਰਬ ਸਾਥ ਹੈਂ ॥੧॥੧੬੧॥
transliteration: Samast Siddh Bridh(i) Daa Sadoov Sarab Saath Hain||1||161||
translation: He is the Donor of all powers and ever accompanies all. 1.161.

gurmukhi: ਅਨਾਥ ਨਾਥ ਨਾਥ ਹੈਂ ਅਭੰਜ ਭੰਜ ਹੈਂ ਸਦਾ ॥
transliteration: Anaath Naath Hain Abhanj Bhanj Hain Sadaa||
translation: He is the Patron of patronless and breaker of the Unbreakable.

gurmukhi: ਅਗੰਗ ਗੰਜ ਗਜੰ ਹੈਂ ਸਦੀਵ ਸਿੱਧ ਬ੍ਰਿਧ ਦਾ ॥
transliteration: Agadj Gadj Hain Sadoov Siddh Bridh Daa||
translation: He is the Donor of treasure to treasureless and also Giver of power.

gurmukhi: ਅਨੂਪ ਰੂਪ ਸਰੂਪ ਹੈਂ ਅਛਿੱਜ ਤੇਜ ਮਾਨੀਅੈਂ ॥
transliteration: Anoop Roop Saroophain Achhijj Tej Maanooain||
translation: His form is unique and His Glory be considered invincible.

gurmukhi: ਸਦੀਵ ਸਿੱਧ ਬੁਧਿ ਦਾ ਪ੍ਰਤਾਪ ਪੱਤ੍ਰ ਜਾਨੀਅੈਂ ॥੨॥੧੬੨॥
transliteration: Sadoov Siddh Budh(i) Daa Prataap Pattra Jaanooain||2||162||
translation: He is the chastiser of powers and is the Splendour-incarnate. 2.162.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਰਾਗ ਰੰਗ ਰੂਪ ਹੈਂ ਨ ਰੋਗ ਰਾਗ ਰੇਥ ਹੈਂ ॥
transliteration: Na Raag Ran Roop Hain Na Rog Raag Rekh Hain||
translation: He is without affection, colour and form and without the ailment, attachment and sign.

gurmukhi: ਅਦੋਖ ਅਦਾਗ ਅਦੱਗ ਹੈਂ ਅਭੂਤ ਅਭਰਮ ਅਭੇਥ ਹੈਂ ॥
transliteration: Adokh Adaag Adagg Hain Abhoog Abharam Abhekh Hain||
translation: He is devoid of blemish, stain and traud, He is without element, illusion and guise.

gurmukhi: ਨ ਤਾਤ ਮਾਤ ਜਾਤ ਹੈਂ ਨ ਪਾਤਿ ਚਿਹਨ ਬਹਨ ਹੈਂ ॥
transliteration: Na Taat Maat Jaat Hain Na Paat(i) Chihar Baran Hain||
translation: He is without father, mother and caste and He is without lineage, mark and colour.

gurmukhi: ਅਦੇਖ ਅਸੇਖ ਅਭੈਖ ਹੈਂ ਸਦੀਵ ਬਿੱਸੁ ਭਰਨ ਹੈਂ ॥੩॥੧੬੩॥
transliteration: Adekh Asekh Abhekh Hain Sadoov Biss(u) Bharan Hain||3||163||
translation: He is Imperceptible, perfect and guiseless and is always the Sustainer of the Universe. 3.163.

gurmukhi: ਬਿਸੂੰਭਰ ਬਿਸੁਨਾਥ ਹੈਂ ਬਿਸੇਥ ਬਿਸ੍ਵ ਭਰਨ ਹੈਂ ॥
transliteration: Bisvanbhar Bisounaath Hain Bisekh Bisva Bharan Hain||
translation: He is the Creator and Master of the Universe and especially its Sustainer.

gurmukhi: ਜਿਮੀ ਜਮਾਨ ਕੇ ਬਿਖੈ ਸਦੀਵ ਕਰਨ ਭਰਨ ਹੈਂ ॥
transliteration: Jimoondjamaan Ke Bhikhai Sadoov Karan Bharan Hain||
translation: Within the earth and the universe, He is always engaged in actions.
